rk infrastructure providers can remotely compete and maintain profitability this is a surprisingly low bar and it is about time networks were designed with this level of large scale optimization cost per mbit maximizing coverage and effective bandwidth available per unit area in any case and for this company s long term plans this type of capability will be absolutely necessary to keep things sane or at least investors find this capability very sexy and compelling especially since we have this lovely visualization engine tied into the system cli batches never have the same effect even if it is more efficient james rogers jamesr best com 